&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Our Advancement team is a collaborative and dynamic group of six full-time staff members, working together to ensure BEAM has the resources to succeed. Building strong, meaningful relationships with funders and supporters is at the heart of what we do. Our funders consist of individuals (50% of revenue), foundations (30%), and corporations (20%).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
