&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Regularly meet with LA STEM Enrichment and Access team to coordinate projects and support one another on key tasks&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Communicate LA team wide updates on the progress of your team’s work and key wins and milestones&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
