&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;We’re launching a pilot after-school math program for 4th graders in NYC, and we’re looking for educators who genuinely enjoy a good logic puzzle.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
